00:49:47.079 --> 00:49:49.949
One last remark for you to
think about.

00:49:49.949 --> 00:49:53.481
Consider the position of the
Israelites in the sixth century,

00:49:53.481 --> 00:49:57.190
the time of the final editing
of the Deuteronomistic history.

00:49:57.190 --> 00:49:59.539
The Israelites are sitting in
exile in Babylon.

00:49:59.539 --> 00:50:02.437
They are trying to make sense
of the tragedy that has befallen

00:50:02.437 --> 00:50:03.909
them, the loss of their land.
 

